dictionary.arrowleftright: Click on the Arrows to page left/right
dictionary.bookmarklater: Select a Category, then a Video to Watch or Bookmark for later
dictionary.clickposterwatch: Click on the Large Poster to watch
dictionary.notesinstruction: Use your keyboard to type notes to yourself, reminders, questions to ask your doctor, things to tell family and friends...anything!
dictionary.notesroomchange: Note: These notes will stay with you for the duration of your visit, unless you change rooms.  If you change rooms, the notes will be deleted.
dictionary.supportinstruction: Use your keyboard to type in the name and telephone number of the primary person you would like us to speak with regarding your care during your hospital stay.  It can be a family member or friend, and you may change the name at any time.
dictionary.videobookmark: Select Bookmark to add the title to My Education.
dictionary.videochosen: These videos have been specifically chosen for you by your clinical team.
dictionary.videoquestion: Ask your nurse if you have any questions about the videos you watch
